  <brief_title>Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacodynamics of QAX028 Compared to Open-label Tiotropium Bromide and Placebo in Mild-to-moderate Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) Patients.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Partially Blinded, Single-dose, Cross-over Proof of Concept Study to Assess the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of QAX028 Compared to Open-label Tiotropium Bromide (Positive Control) and Placebo in Mild-to-moderate COPD Patients</official_title>
