  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This will be a single dose Proof-of-Concept study in mild-to-moderate COPD patients. The
      study will investigate the safety and tolerability of QAX028 as well as the bronchodilatory
      effects of QAX028 compared to tiotropium and placebo in mild-to-moderate COPD patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
